snippet.title: Wallace and Gromit: The Grand Getaway - Official Reveal Trailer | Future Games Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Aardman's dynamic duo Wallace and Gromit return to the gaming scene with a brand-new VR title set on a distant planet. Wallace and Gromit: The Grand Getaway comes to Meta Quest in 2023.

#IGN #SoG #VR
